Revision log:
=============
2012.06.08 - v0.1
Occasionally started just to memorize the letter names, blind typing trainer prototype is ready.
Features:
- html/css-based hebrew keyboard with qwerty markers and cyrillic letter names
- aleph-bet queue as a test one
- next letter highlighting both in queue and on keyboard
- a very little bit of jquery visual effects
Known issues:
- no settings or customization except for the hacking the source code
- nothing happens when input queue ends
- nothing happens when typo occurs
